Duration vs Period
Duration represents a time-based amount (hours,minutes,Seconds)
Period represents a date-based amount (years,months,days)

Duration is compatible with LocalTime as well as LocalDateTime.
period is only compatible with localDate

ZonedDateTime
It represents a Date and time along with a Time Zone
It is used when you want to handle Date and time across diffrent time zones

